sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Envoy as Gateway (Envoy)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant AuthProxy as kube-auth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS (Service CA)
    participant OAuth as OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant AppSvc as Application Service<br/>varies HTTP/HTTPS

    Note over User,AppSvc: Flow 1: User Authentication via Gateway (OAuth Mode)

    User->>Router: GET /dashboard<br/>HTTPS/443, No Auth
    Router->>Envoy: Forward request
    Envoy->>AuthProxy: ext_authz check<br/>HTTPS/8443, Cookie (_oauth2_proxy)
    AuthProxy-->>Envoy: 302 Redirect (no cookie)
    Envoy-->>User: 302 → OAuth login
    User->>OAuth: Login page<br/>HTTPS/443, User credentials
    OAuth-->>User: 302 + Authorization code
    User->>Envoy: GET /oauth2/callback<br/>HTTPS/443, Auth code
    Envoy->>AuthProxy: ext_authz callback<br/>HTTPS/8443
    AuthProxy->>OAuth: Exchange code for token<br/>HTTPS/443, OAuthClient creds
    OAuth-->>AuthProxy: Access token + refresh token
    AuthProxy-->>Envoy: Set cookie (_oauth2_proxy)
    Envoy-->>User: Set-Cookie + redirect to original URL
    User->>Envoy: GET /dashboard<br/>HTTPS/443, Cookie
    Envoy->>AuthProxy: ext_authz validate<br/>HTTPS/8443, Cookie
    AuthProxy-->>Envoy: 200 OK + x-forwarded-access-token
    Note over Envoy: Lua filter: extract access token,<br/>strip _oauth2_proxy cookies
    Envoy->>AppSvc: Forward request<br/>Bearer Token (access token)
    AppSvc-->>Envoy: Response
    Envoy-->>User: Response

    Note over User,AppSvc: Flow 2: Component Deployment via DSC

    participant Admin as Cluster Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DSCCtrl as DSC Controller<br/>ServiceAccount token
    participant CompCtrl as Component Controller<br/>ServiceAccount token

    Admin->>K8sAPI: Create/Update DataScienceCluster CR<br/>HTTPS/6443, Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>DSCCtrl: Watch event (DSC changed)
    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Component CR<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>CompCtrl: Watch event (Component CR)
    CompCtrl->>K8sAPI: Server-side apply manifests<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA token
    CompCtrl->>K8sAPI: Update Component status<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>DSCCtrl: Watch event (Component status)
    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Aggregate → update DSC status<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA token

    Note over User,AppSvc: Flow 3: Monitoring Stack Data Collection

    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>(MonitoringStack)
    participant OTELCol as OTEL Collector
    participant TempoSvc as Tempo<br/>4317/TCP gRPC
    participant ThanosQ as ThanosQuerier<br/>9090/TCP HTTP
    participant PersesSvc as Perses

    Prom->>AppSvc: Scrape metrics<br/>varies HTTP/HTTPS, SA token
    OTELCol->>AppSvc: Collect traces<br/>varies gRPC/HTTP
    OTELCol->>TempoSvc: Export traces<br/>gRPC/4317, TLS optional
    ThanosQ->>Prom: Query metrics<br/>HTTP/9090, SA token
    PersesSvc->>Prom: Query datasource<br/>HTTP, SA token
    PersesSvc->>TempoSvc: Query traces<br/>HTTP, SA token
